reviewText: THIS IS NOT ONLY A GREAT PAIR! IT'S A MUST SEE MOVIES FOR EVERYONE! YOU WILL NOT BE DISAPOINTED!
its a dvd, works. what can u say about a dvd. movie movies have already been reviewed so u know what u are getting.

I liked both movies.  I have seen them both on TV several times and decided to order this 2 pack for a very reasonable price from Amazon.  I'm not going to review each film here, but the newer CONTAGION is a much better film and more realistic in what  would happen and how people will react - bringing out the  best and worst in human beings if such a global event were to occur!
both of these movies give a view into how a pandemic could play out, including the quarantine measures put in place by the government.  makes me always stock up on more supplies :)
outbreak works fine but contagion won't play.
Both great movies. I share them with my pathology classes.
Loved the Outbreak movie but Contagion was just ok.
